  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Use React Native primitives or Expo Router. Apply Tailwind classes via NativeWind. Ensure generous padding (`p-4` or `p-6`) and border-radius (`rounded-2xl` for cards, `rounded-xl` for buttons) for a modern, tactile mobile app feel. Include `data-testid` on all interactive elements (buttons, inputs, tabs). Use Phosphor Icons for iconography. Stick to the provided warm color palette and avoid using system default blues/purples. Provide image sources from the exact URLs specified in this JSON for authentic placeholder data."
